1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 26=

3
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,679
Hurry, go.

4
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,479
Go.

5
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,009
- What is going on here?
- Meng, Bei.

6
00:01:41,010 --> 00:01:42,850
- Du.
- Go.

7
00:01:43,010 --> 00:01:44,720
Meng.

8
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,280
- It is okay, Du.
- Meng.

9
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,039
Chief Judge Shu, tell me,

10
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:55,289
how many years
would a child trafficker get?

11
00:01:55,290 --> 00:01:56,280
Well...

12
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,800
May I take a look?

13
00:02:13,730 --> 00:02:18,970
(Name: Mr. Wang. Contact Number)

14
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:20,840
Are you Wang Yuanbao?

15
00:02:22,130 --> 00:02:23,330
Dad.

16
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,640
Yuanbao.

17
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:26,290
Yuanbao.

18
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:29,010
Slow down.

19
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:30,919
Ms. Shu.

20
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,599
Hello?

21
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,890
Xiezhi,

22
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,569
come over here right away.

23
00:02:34,570 --> 00:02:35,799
Yuanbao is with me.

24
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,199
With you?

25
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,169
How is he with you?

26
00:02:38,170 --> 00:02:39,450
Keep an eye on him.

27
00:02:40,290 --> 00:02:41,849
Sir, madam, Yuanbao has been found.

28
00:02:41,850 --> 00:02:43,010
Found?

29
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,640
Where?

30
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:47,090
(Jinghongyuan Park)

31
00:02:47,170 --> 00:02:48,570
So close.

32
00:02:50,250 --> 00:02:50,889
Come with me.

33
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:52,570
Okay, let us go.

34
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,520
Sir, madam, we found him. Come quickly.

35
00:02:57,570 --> 00:02:58,599
Okay.

36
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,360
How did you get here so fast?

37
00:03:00,730 --> 00:03:02,450
We happened to be searching nearby.

38
00:03:02,970 --> 00:03:04,680
- How did you find Yuanbao?
- He is over there.

39
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:06,730
Thanks to Ms. Qin.

40
00:03:06,890 --> 00:03:09,129
I was helping Ms. Shu
look for the other two children,

41
00:03:09,130 --> 00:03:10,319
and we ran into him here.

42
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,359
Did I not tell you to wait at home?
Why did you run out?

43
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,009
You scared the two of us to death.

44
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:14,759
Exactly.

45
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,799
We agreed on this,
but you would not listen.

46
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,729
We told you clearly,

47
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:18,849
and you still ran out by yourself.

48
00:03:18,850 --> 00:03:19,729
No need.

49
00:03:19,730 --> 00:03:20,599
What do you mean no need?

50
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,639
I am telling you, Yuanbao,

51
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,290
if you run around like this again,

52
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:25,009
we really will not want you anymore!

53
00:03:25,010 --> 00:03:25,639
Sir.

54
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,290
Dad!

55
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:32,240
Ms. Shu.

56
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,680
Are you all right?

57
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,199
Yuanbao.

58
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:35,519
My waist.

59
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,039
Slowly.

60
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,240
Get up.

61
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:40,920
Careful.

62
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,449
Dad, Dad...

63
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:44,599
Does not want me anymore.

64
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,199
Yuanbao.

65
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,640
Does not want me anymore.

66
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,520
Does not want me anymore.

67
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,120
Yuanbao.

68
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,409
Do not run, slow down.

69
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:55,289
It is okay.

70
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:56,840
This child, honestly.

71
00:03:57,970 --> 00:03:58,639
Dad.

72
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,199
Yuanbao.

73
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,010
Dad does not want me anymore.

74
00:04:11,690 --> 00:04:14,210
All right.

75
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,929
I will stay right here,

76
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:17,009
I will not come closer, okay?

77
00:04:17,010 --> 00:04:18,319
Do not get upset, all right, Yuanbao?

78
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,520
Yuanbao.

79
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:27,049
There he is.

80
00:04:27,050 --> 00:04:27,489
Go.

81
00:04:27,490 --> 00:04:28,129
Yuanbao.

82
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:29,199
Whatever it is,

83
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,609
we can go home and talk it through.

84
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:33,009
When we get home, I will buy you
your favorite candied hawthorn, okay?

85
00:04:33,010 --> 00:04:34,569
If you jump from there today,

86
00:04:34,570 --> 00:04:35,809
it will hurt a lot,

87
00:04:35,810 --> 00:04:37,930
and it will not solve anything.

88
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,369
It will only make your parents,

89
00:04:39,370 --> 00:04:40,690
who love you, heartbroken.

90
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,159
Yuanbao, what are you doing?

91
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,810
Get down from there.

92
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,400
Dad.

93
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,639
Dad... Dad.

94
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,009
Sir, madam,

95
00:04:48,010 --> 00:04:49,129
please stay right there.

96
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,929
Do not provoke him.
Let me calm him down.

97
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:52,640
Trust me, okay?

98
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,959
Listen,

99
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,400
we should follow Judge Shen's lead.

100
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,759
Do not go over there
and make things worse.

101
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,279
Yuanbao.

102
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:57,689
Dad.

103
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:58,929
Yuanbao.

104
00:04:58,930 --> 00:05:00,249
Yuanbao, listen to me.

105
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:01,690
Listen to me, Yuanbao.

106
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,639
Yuanbao.

107
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,009
Do you know

108
00:05:04,010 --> 00:05:06,130
why your parents named you Yuanbao?

109
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,399
It is because they hope

110
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:10,280
to always cherish you like a treasure.

111
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:13,399
Dad... Dad, no.

112
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,889
Does not want me anymore.

113
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:16,489
How could your father leave you?

114
00:05:16,490 --> 00:05:17,640
Yuanbao.

115
00:05:18,450 --> 00:05:20,890
Your father loves you deeply.

116
00:05:20,930 --> 00:05:22,569
Your father's legs
are not in good condition,

117
00:05:22,570 --> 00:05:24,809
yet he still walks with you
every day and plays with you,

118
00:05:24,810 --> 00:05:26,690
doing his best to be there for you.

119
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,129
You do not want to see him sad, right?

120
00:05:29,130 --> 00:05:29,839
Yuanbao.

121
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,959
I also heard,

122
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,330
I heard your father say,

123
00:05:32,610 --> 00:05:34,129
there was a time when he was ill,

124
00:05:34,130 --> 00:05:36,639
and you stayed by his side, right?

125
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,489
You kept calling out to him.

126
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:40,600
Yuanbao loves Dad too, right?

127
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:43,199
Your father heard it all.
He told me everything.

128
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,609
Come here.

129
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:47,040
When we get home, he will buy you
your favorite candied hawthorn.

130
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:49,450
Dad.

131
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:53,929
Are you okay?

132
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:54,959
How is he?

133
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:57,959
Your father will not scold you.
I am a judge.

134
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,249
I promise you,

135
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:00,079
from now on,

136
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,929
your father will not scold you anymore.

137
00:06:01,930 --> 00:06:02,449
Okay?

138
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:04,080
A judge would not lie.

139
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,959
Yuanbao.

140
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,839
Dad will not scold you anymore.

141
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,370
Let us go home.

142
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:11,640
Go home.

143
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:12,960
Yuanbao.

144
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,210
Come, come here.

145
00:06:16,690 --> 00:06:17,720
Come.

146
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,399
Come.

147
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,480
Good boy.

148
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,759
Yes, that is right.

149
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,890
Come over.

150
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,960
Come, come.

151
00:06:37,930 --> 00:06:39,250
Come, come here.

152
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,370
Come.

153
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,600
Watch your head.

154
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,689
Sir.

155
00:06:45,690 --> 00:06:47,330
Yuanbao is a good boy.

156
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,249
Sir.

157
00:06:49,250 --> 00:06:50,770
What is wrong? Sir.

158
00:06:50,930 --> 00:06:53,080
Dad... Dad.

159
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,040
Yuanbao.

160
00:07:19,770 --> 00:07:22,130
(Emergency Room)

161
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,810
Dad, please do not worry.

162
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:48,719
(Emergency Room)

163
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,249
Dad, please do not worry.

164
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:52,210
How long has it been?

165
00:07:52,370 --> 00:07:53,640
I know.

166
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,129
Why are you here?

167
00:07:59,130 --> 00:08:00,690
I just finished surgery.

168
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,600
He went in five minutes ago.

169
00:08:11,450 --> 00:08:15,850
(Emergency Room)

170
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:21,089
(Inpatient Department)

171
00:08:21,090 --> 00:08:23,770
(Ward 2, Beds V6-V8)

172
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:41,000
Shen Xiezhi,

173
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:46,080
can you hear me?

174
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:07,170
♪When a leaf can't find a place to fall♪

175
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:09,849
♪Just like me♪

176
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:13,200
♪Wandering without a destination♪

177
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,759
Why is it you?

178
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:21,430
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

179
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,989
♪I've decided♪

180
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:27,160
♪To stay by your side♪

181
00:09:29,570 --> 00:09:34,020
♪Become your soaring wings♪

182
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,240
Here.

183
00:09:43,330 --> 00:09:44,129
How is it?

184
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:46,839
♪I want to be in your world♪

185
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:50,409
♪And cast away my disguise♪

186
00:09:50,410 --> 00:09:56,990
♪Lean on my tender shoulder♪

187
00:09:57,270 --> 00:10:00,949
♪I want to be in your world♪

188
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:04,569
♪I'll be your shelter♪

189
00:10:04,570 --> 00:10:11,150
♪I'll be there for you
until the very end♪

190
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:30,789
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

191
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,150
Hold me tight.

192
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,539
♪I've decided♪

193
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:37,920
♪To stay by your side♪

194
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:44,970
♪Become your soaring wings♪

195
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:53,320
♪Let me be your safe haven♪

196
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:56,600
I want to be the one
who always takes care of you.

197
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,170
But I am conflicted.

198
00:10:58,610 --> 00:11:00,290
I do not want us to repeat what happened

199
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,530
to Jiang Feng and Lou Yue.

200
00:11:07,950 --> 00:11:11,529
♪I want to be in your world♪

201
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:15,099
♪I'll be your shelter♪

202
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:21,950
♪I'll be there for you
until the very end♪

203
00:11:22,130 --> 00:11:25,699
♪I want to be in your world♪

204
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:29,279
♪And forget the passage of time♪

205
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:36,189
♪You are the only one that I see♪

206
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:39,839
♪I want to be in your world♪

207
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:43,349
♪Everything is no longer faraway♪

208
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:49,919
♪I'll be there for you
until the very end♪

209
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:53,489
♪I want to be in your world♪

210
00:11:53,490 --> 00:11:57,109
♪And cast away my disguise♪

211
00:11:57,110 --> 00:12:04,260
♪Lean on my tender shoulder♪

212
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:18,639
Do you feel better now?

213
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,880
Much better.

214
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,519
Come.

215
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,720
Slowly.

216
00:12:22,850 --> 00:12:24,840
Careful. One, two.

217
00:12:27,010 --> 00:12:29,330
You should stop running back and forth.

218
00:12:29,890 --> 00:12:31,530
Focus on taking care of the shop.

219
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:34,650
You have not fully recovered yet.

220
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:37,170
I can just order takeout.

221
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,849
Why eat takeout?

222
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:41,080
I do not trust food made by others.

223
00:12:42,130 --> 00:12:43,639
After you finish eating,

224
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,329
just leave it.

225
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:46,170
I will come back later to clean up.

226
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:48,519
I will be leaving soon.
The mutton soup shop is still busy.

227
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:50,489
Take it slow.

228
00:12:50,490 --> 00:12:51,439
I know.

229
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,600
I am heading out.

230
00:13:18,970 --> 00:13:20,410
Why did you come out?

231
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:21,329
Careful.

232
00:13:21,330 --> 00:13:22,480
I am going to the restroom.

233
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:25,240
Slowly.

234
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,930
What is wrong, sweetheart?

235
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,329
I will get you some hot water.

236
00:13:38,330 --> 00:13:39,650
No.

237
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:44,530
I did not throw up.

238
00:13:49,010 --> 00:13:50,360
Xiao,

239
00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:51,679
do you know

240
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:54,480
why I have always
been worried about having a child?

241
00:13:59,090 --> 00:14:00,650
Because I am afraid.

242
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:04,209
I am afraid I cannot
take on that responsibility,

243
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:06,760
and that I will not be a good mother.

244
00:14:11,010 --> 00:14:13,050
But now I have figured it out.

245
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:16,480
No matter what our baby is like,

246
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:19,840
whether beautiful or not, smart or not,

247
00:14:20,010 --> 00:14:21,810
he will still be our baby.

248
00:14:22,610 --> 00:14:25,600
And I will do my very best

249
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:26,799
to let him grow up happy

250
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,690
and healthy.

251
00:14:29,330 --> 00:14:31,009
I think as long as there is love and joy

252
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:32,559
between us and our child,

253
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:34,720
then I will be a good mother.

254
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:36,410
Right?

255
00:14:40,330 --> 00:14:41,679
Do not worry.

256
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:44,080
We will definitely be good parents.

257
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:46,170
You have to trust me

258
00:14:46,330 --> 00:14:47,720
and trust yourself.

259
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:57,489
Ms. Qin,

260
00:14:57,490 --> 00:14:59,039
what should I do?

261
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:00,919
What happened?

262
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:02,600
This is punishment.

263
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:04,290
It is punishment.

264
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,489
Back then, my mother was beaten,

265
00:15:06,490 --> 00:15:08,120
her head covered in blood.

266
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:11,330
I was timid, I was weak.

267
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:13,450
I did nothing.

268
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:16,209
Now it is my turn.

269
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:18,000
This is my punishment.

270
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:19,039
Yajun, listen to me.

271
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,840
Do not think like that.

272
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:23,450
Domestic violence is absolutely wrong.

273
00:15:23,490 --> 00:15:25,759
It has nothing to do with you.
This is not your fault.

274
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:28,249
When facing domestic violence,

275
00:15:28,250 --> 00:15:29,969
even adults would feel terrified,

276
00:15:29,970 --> 00:15:31,039
let alone a child.

277
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,609
Besides,

278
00:15:31,610 --> 00:15:33,480
you were really young at the time.

279
00:15:34,090 --> 00:15:35,799
Your mother did not protect you well.

280
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,129
That was not your responsibility.

281
00:15:37,130 --> 00:15:39,559
And now that you have
your own child, your own daughter,

282
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,679
do not repeat your mother's path.

283
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,439
Can I really do it?

284
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,050
Of course you can.

285
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,559
Remember this,

286
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:49,559
if you ever need help,

287
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:51,559
you can come
to Chenxi Legal Aid Center anytime.

288
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:53,530
There is always someone there,
24 hours a day.

289
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:56,439
Thank you, Ms. Qin.

290
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,600
Okay.

291
00:16:03,010 --> 00:16:05,209
Ms. Qin, you are impressive now.

292
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:06,559
Paid consultations on one hand,

293
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,969
legal aid on the other.

294
00:16:07,970 --> 00:16:08,889
You have achieved

295
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:11,209
both financial and personal fulfillment.

296
00:16:11,210 --> 00:16:13,240
It is not as exaggerated as you say.

297
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,129
I just believe

298
00:16:15,130 --> 00:16:16,489
that if I can help one more person,

299
00:16:16,490 --> 00:16:17,840
then I will help one more.

300
00:16:18,090 --> 00:16:19,039
That is also

301
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:21,009
the reason I became
a lawyer in the first place.

302
00:16:21,010 --> 00:16:24,010
(Inpatient Department)

303
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:43,690
(Mediation Room 1 In Use)

304
00:16:58,490 --> 00:16:59,930
Mom.

305
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,289
I am telling you,

306
00:17:12,290 --> 00:17:14,849
- soaking your feet every day is best for your health.
- It is fine.

307
00:17:14,850 --> 00:17:16,370
I do not think it helps.

308
00:17:17,770 --> 00:17:19,170
I have already

309
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,090
sorted your medicine.

310
00:17:21,370 --> 00:17:23,609
Make sure to take it on time
and in the right amounts.

311
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:24,639
Let us work together.

312
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,919
We will definitely get through this.

313
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,930
(The Emergence
and Development of Economic Law)

314
00:17:36,370 --> 00:17:38,930
(Printing document)

315
00:17:41,330 --> 00:17:43,210
Please sign here, both of you.

316
00:18:08,770 --> 00:18:11,650
(Inpatient Department)

317
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:24,670
(Divorce Agreement:
Husband, Lian Yongjiu. Wife, Shu Jing)

318
00:18:29,810 --> 00:18:31,090
You are here.

319
00:18:32,850 --> 00:18:34,170
Well,

320
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:38,089
Fei said she wanted
to have lamb at home today,

321
00:18:38,090 --> 00:18:39,410
so I

322
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,520
came early to prepare.

323
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,000
Actually...

324
00:18:47,570 --> 00:18:49,240
Actually, it is me who wants to eat it.

325
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,650
I know.

326
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:54,639
I knew from the first day I met you

327
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,280
that you liked lamb.

328
00:18:58,370 --> 00:19:00,240
Then we had Fei,

329
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:02,040
and she liked it too.

330
00:19:07,610 --> 00:19:09,000
Later,

331
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,240
I quit my job.

332
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:13,650
Since I was going
to start a business anyway,

333
00:19:13,850 --> 00:19:16,000
I might as well open a mutton soup shop.

334
00:19:16,890 --> 00:19:18,610
I have never thought

335
00:19:19,090 --> 00:19:21,320
that opening a mutton soup shop
was beneath you.

336
00:19:22,570 --> 00:19:24,760
I just feel that all these years,

337
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,479
you have sacrificed too much.

338
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,280
You had bigger ambitions,

339
00:19:29,130 --> 00:19:30,850
you could have lived a better life.

340
00:19:31,370 --> 00:19:32,760
Why

341
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:34,849
choose to spend your life
around a pot of soup?

342
00:19:34,850 --> 00:19:36,650
I do not see it as a sacrifice.

343
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,280
What is marriage?

344
00:19:42,130 --> 00:19:43,529
At its core,

345
00:19:43,530 --> 00:19:45,610
marriage is about two people

346
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,560
supporting each other

347
00:19:47,770 --> 00:19:49,170
and accepting each other.

348
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,850
No matter what,

349
00:19:54,050 --> 00:19:56,610
I am willing to do all this for you,

350
00:19:57,050 --> 00:19:59,450
and for this family.

351
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:07,720
Some time ago,

352
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:09,800
when I was injured,

353
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:14,690
you took such good care of me.

354
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,370
I felt

355
00:20:20,890 --> 00:20:23,210
very guilty.

356
00:20:24,530 --> 00:20:27,410
I should not
have forced my will onto you.

357
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,720
Lian,

358
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:40,240
I am sorry.

359
00:20:47,090 --> 00:20:48,890
I do not want to lose you.

360
00:20:55,370 --> 00:20:57,450
It is okay. After all,

361
00:20:58,850 --> 00:21:01,480
you are Chief Judge Shu.

362
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:04,040
Even if you were to enforce it on me,

363
00:21:04,330 --> 00:21:06,130
I would still accept it.

364
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:10,480
Having you by my side,

365
00:21:11,090 --> 00:21:13,560
watching Fei grow up together,

366
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,760
and living each day

367
00:21:15,770 --> 00:21:18,560
with ease and happiness,

368
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,090
that is what I want.

369
00:22:25,810 --> 00:22:27,280
Shen Xiezhi,

370
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,930
did we not agree

371
00:22:33,130 --> 00:22:35,000
that I would wait for you after work?

372
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:40,000
Why did you not keep your promise?

373
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,410
Wait for me.

374
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,690
Wait for me to come back.

375
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,720
I have even thought about it,

376
00:22:51,290 --> 00:22:54,040
we would go to so many places together,

377
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:57,850
and do so many things together.

378
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:06,090
When will you wake up?

379
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,800
You even said

380
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,720
you would take care of me.

381
00:23:25,530 --> 00:23:27,410
Now it is my turn to take care of you.

382
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,560
Shen Xiezhi.

383
00:23:45,890 --> 00:23:47,090
Doctor.

384
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,520
Doctor!

385
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:54,130
- Doctor!
- Calling. Please wait.

386
00:23:55,810 --> 00:23:57,280
Shen Xiezhi.

387
00:24:01,370 --> 00:24:01,809
Doctor.

388
00:24:01,810 --> 00:24:02,199
What is it?

389
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,890
Come in quickly. He just moved.

390
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:07,520
Miss, please wait outside.

391
00:24:14,330 --> 00:24:15,610
Judge Shen is awake.

392
00:24:16,610 --> 00:24:17,719
He is awake. Judge Shen is awake.

393
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,769
- That is great.
- That is great.

394
00:24:18,770 --> 00:24:21,369
- He is really awake.
- Judge Shen is finally awake.

395
00:24:21,370 --> 00:24:22,399
Really?

396
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,800
Judge Shen is awake.

397
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:24,569
When did this happen?

398
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:25,369
We just got the call.

399
00:24:25,370 --> 00:24:27,719
Then how about this,
after work we all go visit him together.

400
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:28,129
Right.

401
00:24:28,130 --> 00:24:29,999
- I am going too.
- Me too.

402
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,480
We will all go, all of us.

403
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,610
Shen Xiezhi.

404
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,240
Who are you?

405
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:01,210
What do you mean?

406
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:07,240
My head hurts so much.

407
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:10,240
My mind is completely blank.

408
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:13,410
There are so many things
I cannot remember.

409
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,760
You forgot everything?

410
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:22,650
I suddenly remember a few things.

411
00:25:23,050 --> 00:25:25,090
Once I went out on an assignment,

412
00:25:25,850 --> 00:25:27,719
and got lost in the mountains.

413
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:29,610
I was trapped there

414
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:32,690
and stayed overnight in a small hut.

415
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:37,690
But the snow that night was beautiful.

416
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:41,439
I still remember.

417
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:44,760
I went with my colleague
to look for a child

418
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,320
named Fei,

419
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,850
and then there was a fire.

420
00:25:49,770 --> 00:25:51,850
I wanted to show what I could do,

421
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:55,450
but I ended up being
the one who got rescued.

422
00:25:58,850 --> 00:26:01,170
I think I also have a girlfriend.

423
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:04,040
Her grandma cooks really well,

424
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:07,610
just a bit heavy on the salt.

425
00:26:08,890 --> 00:26:10,890
What is my girlfriend's name?

426
00:26:14,290 --> 00:26:15,930
I cannot remember.

427
00:26:16,530 --> 00:26:18,410
What did you say her name was?

428
00:26:19,130 --> 00:26:20,850
What is wrong with you?

429
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,479
Your boyfriend is injured,

430
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,690
and which girlfriend would be so rough?

431
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,760
I am awake now,

432
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,690
and instead of hugging me,

433
00:26:33,090 --> 00:26:34,450
you are just standing there crying.

434
00:26:39,890 --> 00:26:41,240
Stop crying.

435
00:26:56,410 --> 00:27:01,450
(Qingcheng District People's Court,
Tianhai City)

436
00:27:01,530 --> 00:27:01,919
Come on.

437
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,369
Hurry up, be careful.

438
00:27:03,370 --> 00:27:04,650
I will ride with you.

439
00:27:05,090 --> 00:27:06,370
Okay.

440
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,399
I am telling you,
this is because you are young.

441
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,289
If it were me,

442
00:27:15,290 --> 00:27:16,850
I would still be lying flat in bed.

443
00:27:17,570 --> 00:27:19,569
Should we have a doctor check you

444
00:27:19,570 --> 00:27:21,560
to see if you can still be a judge?

445
00:27:22,810 --> 00:27:25,569
Of course I can. No need to test.

446
00:27:25,570 --> 00:27:27,289
Do not worry, I am fine.

447
00:27:27,290 --> 00:27:29,329
I remember everything that happened.

448
00:27:29,330 --> 00:27:30,960
Even though my eyes were closed,

449
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:33,520
just look at the flowers by the bed,

450
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:36,159
they were changed every day.

451
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:38,719
The frequency was too high.
What a waste.

452
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,399
And also,

453
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,809
my shameless friend

454
00:27:40,810 --> 00:27:42,439
brought his girlfriend to the hospital.

455
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:45,450
I am in this condition, and he is still
showing off his relationship in front of me.

456
00:27:47,850 --> 00:27:49,999
What bothers me the most is

457
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,479
someone comes to the hospital
every day to complain,

458
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:54,129
not even letting me
have a peaceful break.

459
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:55,480
You...

460
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:58,040
And then there is someone saying
I did not keep my promise.

461
00:27:59,130 --> 00:28:00,529
Now that I am awake,

462
00:28:00,530 --> 00:28:02,000
I will keep my promise.

463
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,399
How is Yuanbao?

464
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,289
Do not worry.

465
00:28:06,290 --> 00:28:08,639
Yuanbao is still waiting
to treat you to candied hawthorn.

466
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:11,199
You have just woken up.
Get some proper rest.

467
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:13,089
Wait until you have fully recovered.

468
00:28:13,090 --> 00:28:14,369
Rest?

469
00:28:14,370 --> 00:28:16,240
I can go back to work right now.

470
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,130
By the way,

471
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:20,049
I did not miss

472
00:28:20,050 --> 00:28:21,999
the reporting date
at the High Court, did I?

473
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,999
All right, do not worry about that.

474
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,320
Focus on recovering.

475
00:28:25,890 --> 00:28:27,369
Well, I would say he is fine.

476
00:28:27,370 --> 00:28:28,919
He is already making jokes, right?

477
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,849
Exactly.

478
00:28:29,850 --> 00:28:31,439
After getting injured this time,

479
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,679
Xiezhi has learned a new skill.

480
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,410
He even knows how to tease people now.

481
00:28:53,930 --> 00:28:55,639
(Certificate of Honor)

482
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,769
Congratulations.

483
00:28:56,770 --> 00:28:58,919
(Qingcheng Court Family Court
Retirement Ceremony)

484
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,320
Thank you.

485
00:29:06,610 --> 00:29:07,569
Today,

486
00:29:07,570 --> 00:29:09,090
I am officially retiring.

487
00:29:09,530 --> 00:29:11,000
Standing here,

488
00:29:11,370 --> 00:29:13,610
I feel both excited and emotional.

489
00:29:13,850 --> 00:29:15,049
Many people say

490
00:29:15,050 --> 00:29:16,399
Family Court

491
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:18,719
is just like a group
of neighborhood aunties,

492
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,159
handling nothing more than

493
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:23,210
petty family matters.

494
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:26,399
I remember back in 2016,

495
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:28,479
President Zhang came to me

496
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:30,960
and said we were going
to establish a Family Court.

497
00:29:31,050 --> 00:29:33,569
He told me that family affairs

498
00:29:33,570 --> 00:29:35,890
are also matters of the nation.

499
00:29:36,890 --> 00:29:38,520
At the time, I thought,

500
00:29:40,050 --> 00:29:42,210
that sounded quite ambitious.

501
00:29:42,770 --> 00:29:44,199
As for me,

502
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:46,329
managing neighborhood matters was fine,

503
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:47,999
but suddenly asking me

504
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,809
to shoulder such a responsibility,

505
00:29:49,810 --> 00:29:51,690
I really felt the pressure.

506
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:55,000
But later,

507
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,930
thanks to all of you.

508
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:59,370
Look at our team,

509
00:29:59,890 --> 00:30:02,280
we have those with
a strong sense of responsibility,

510
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,930
those who are attentive and thoughtful,

511
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,760
and you, the girl who cries easily.

512
00:30:08,610 --> 00:30:09,890
Mr. He.

513
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:12,769
And even a little "beast,"

514
00:30:12,770 --> 00:30:14,289
that is what you all call him, right?

515
00:30:14,290 --> 00:30:16,000
Yes.

516
00:30:16,850 --> 00:30:18,609
It is because of all of you,

517
00:30:18,610 --> 00:30:21,199
using your intelligence and dedication,

518
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,849
that we have fully brought out

519
00:30:22,850 --> 00:30:25,289
the initiative of our judges,

520
00:30:25,290 --> 00:30:26,199
while

521
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,239
also protecting

522
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:29,520
the families of the people
in Qingcheng District,

523
00:30:29,530 --> 00:30:32,410
and safeguarding
the harmony of our society.

524
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,130
Next week,

525
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:37,090
I will go to the retirees' center

526
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,399
to report

527
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:39,800
to President Zhang

528
00:30:39,810 --> 00:30:41,410
that the task he entrusted to me

529
00:30:41,570 --> 00:30:43,610
has been successfully completed.

530
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,090
From now on, this responsibility

531
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:48,240
will be passed on to you, Ms. Shu.

532
00:30:58,570 --> 00:30:59,399
Tell me,

533
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:02,529
are you satisfied with our staffing
and resource allocation?

534
00:31:02,530 --> 00:31:03,720
Satisfied.

535
00:31:03,810 --> 00:31:04,889
From now on,

536
00:31:04,890 --> 00:31:07,410
you will have to handle
any problems on your own.

537
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,369
Do not come looking for me,

538
00:31:08,370 --> 00:31:10,049
and do not blame me
for leaving you a mess.

539
00:31:10,050 --> 00:31:11,320
I would not.

540
00:31:13,530 --> 00:31:15,719
President Chen, you know

541
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,089
Shu Jing's abilities.

542
00:31:17,090 --> 00:31:18,369
There will be no problem at all.

543
00:31:18,370 --> 00:31:20,919
Under Ms. Shu's leadership,
please keep working hard.

544
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,000
All right.

545
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,809
Shen has returned as well.

546
00:31:44,810 --> 00:31:47,560
It is rare for our Family Court
to gather this completely.

547
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:48,679
Thank you.

548
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:49,930
All right.

549
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,959
Not bad.

550
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:52,439
Smells great.

551
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,129
All right, let us get ready, let us...

552
00:31:54,130 --> 00:31:55,280
Come on,

553
00:31:55,370 --> 00:31:56,199
let us raise our glasses.

554
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,370
Grandpa.

555
00:31:57,480 --> 00:31:58,800
Fei.

556
00:31:58,810 --> 00:32:00,370
Your longevity noodles.

557
00:32:01,130 --> 00:32:02,439
But today is not my birthday.

558
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,809
Why give me longevity noodles?

559
00:32:03,810 --> 00:32:05,760
Wishing you a long life.

560
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:08,639
Just hearing you say that,

561
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:10,800
I would gladly
eat these noodles every day.

562
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:14,040
Fei, come, sit down and eat with us.
Sit next to Mom.

563
00:32:16,050 --> 00:32:17,890
Pour Fei a drink.

564
00:32:18,850 --> 00:32:20,239
Happy retirement.

565
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:23,809
Happy retirement.

566
00:32:23,810 --> 00:32:24,639
Thank you, everyone.

567
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:25,529
Mr. He,

568
00:32:25,530 --> 00:32:27,800
may you begin a wonderful new chapter.

569
00:32:28,290 --> 00:32:28,999
Mr. He,

570
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:29,849
you are about to live

571
00:32:29,850 --> 00:32:31,329
the life I have always dreamed of.

572
00:32:31,330 --> 00:32:32,129
Not quite.

573
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:34,609
Though the evening sun may be late,
it still fills the sky with glow.

574
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:35,959
You will keep contributing.

575
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:36,960
It's a must.

576
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,769
Just do not get too carried away
with square dancing.

577
00:32:38,770 --> 00:32:40,159
Remember to come back
and visit us often.

578
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,479
Of course.

579
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:43,329
If Mr. He ever goes square dancing,

580
00:32:43,330 --> 00:32:46,280
he will be
the most handsome elder there.

581
00:32:46,290 --> 00:32:48,210
- That is right.
- Who are you calling an elder?

582
00:32:48,330 --> 00:32:50,089
A distinguished middle-aged gentleman.

583
00:32:50,090 --> 00:32:50,959
Yes.

584
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:53,930
Come, let us toast to
the most handsome gentleman.

585
00:32:54,290 --> 00:32:55,719
Come, thank you, everyone.

586
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,129
Come, together.

587
00:32:57,130 --> 00:32:59,399
Come, together.

588
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,720
Thank you, everyone.

589
00:33:02,090 --> 00:33:03,650
Let me also make a toast.

590
00:33:03,890 --> 00:33:05,049
Boss Lian,

591
00:33:05,050 --> 00:33:07,889
when I first interned at the court,

592
00:33:07,890 --> 00:33:09,609
I spent over half a year

593
00:33:09,610 --> 00:33:10,569
under Mr. He's guidance.

594
00:33:10,570 --> 00:33:11,849
That is right.

595
00:33:11,850 --> 00:33:14,560
So I must call Mr. He my mentor.

596
00:33:14,570 --> 00:33:15,849
Although I have now changed careers

597
00:33:15,850 --> 00:33:17,439
and become a cook,

598
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,999
when I go out,

599
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:20,930
I hardly dare mention my mentor's name.

600
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:22,569
Come, mentor,

601
00:33:22,570 --> 00:33:24,399
I wish you a happy retirement.

602
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,849
Boss Lian, as the saying goes,
every profession has its master.

603
00:33:26,850 --> 00:33:28,529
I wish your business great success

604
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:29,999
and continued prosperity.

605
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,480
- Thank you, mentor.
- Come.

606
00:33:31,570 --> 00:33:32,800
I will drink this.

607
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,889
This second toast,

608
00:33:36,890 --> 00:33:38,049
I raise it to all of you.

609
00:33:38,050 --> 00:33:40,889
Thank you all for always
supporting my small shop.

610
00:33:40,890 --> 00:33:42,850
Thank you, everyone.

611
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:45,329
Wishing you booming business.

612
00:33:45,330 --> 00:33:46,760
May your business
grow bigger and bigger.

613
00:33:50,050 --> 00:33:51,610
As for this third toast,

614
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:53,610
I want to toast our family leader.

615
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,769
From now on,

616
00:33:55,770 --> 00:33:58,040
our family will rely on Chief Judge Shu

617
00:33:58,440 --> 00:34:00,040
to bring honor to us.

618
00:34:00,890 --> 00:34:03,240
All right, go serve the dishes already.

619
00:34:03,330 --> 00:34:03,569
No,

620
00:34:03,570 --> 00:34:06,199
then should you
not have a cross-cup toast?

621
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:12,729
Cross-cup!

622
00:34:12,730 --> 00:34:16,039
Cross-cup!

623
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:16,849
Wait.

624
00:34:16,850 --> 00:34:18,400
Cross-cup!

625
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:20,169
Everyone, raise your glasses together.

626
00:34:20,170 --> 00:34:21,530
To Mr. He,

627
00:34:21,690 --> 00:34:22,689
happy retirement.

628
00:34:22,690 --> 00:34:23,649
Come, everyone together.

629
00:34:23,650 --> 00:34:24,439
Come.

630
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:26,559
To everyone here,

631
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:28,439
may we all do better and better. Cheers.

632
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:31,119
Cheers.

633
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:35,730
(Lian Mutton Soup)

634
00:34:46,610 --> 00:34:52,090
(Tianhai High People's Court)

635
00:34:52,650 --> 00:34:54,800
Hello, please show your ID.

636
00:35:03,730 --> 00:35:04,559
This way, please.

637
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:05,800
Thank you.

638
00:35:06,490 --> 00:35:10,330
(Tianhai High People's Court)

639
00:35:18,450 --> 00:35:23,610
(Political Department)

640
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,720
Come in.

641
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:28,999
Hello.

642
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:29,889
Hello.

643
00:35:29,890 --> 00:35:31,519
I am Shen Xiezhi,

644
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:32,559
a judge from the Family Court

645
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:33,880
of Qingcheng Court.

646
00:35:34,690 --> 00:35:35,880
Come in.

647
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:37,360
Ms. Lou.

648
00:35:38,770 --> 00:35:39,970
Here.

649
00:35:41,210 --> 00:35:44,479
This is the bank contract, and these are
the other related documents.

650
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,039
Please let me know

651
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,400
if anything else is needed.

652
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,039
Just leave them here.

653
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,610
I trust your work.

654
00:35:52,250 --> 00:35:53,490
There is one more thing.

655
00:35:53,690 --> 00:35:54,809
Mr. Xu from Yuehua Technology

656
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:56,399
has a will dispute

657
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,880
and has entrusted it to me.

658
00:35:58,040 --> 00:35:59,729
He wants me to assign a lawyer

659
00:35:59,730 --> 00:36:00,769
with extensive experience

660
00:36:00,770 --> 00:36:02,720
in family law litigation.

661
00:36:03,290 --> 00:36:03,959
About this,

662
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:06,010
I should have discussed it
with you earlier.

663
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:08,320
Recently, you have assigned me
to non-litigation work.

664
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:10,840
Actually, I find non-litigation
quite interesting.

665
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,999
From now on, I plan to focus
on non-litigation practice.

666
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:13,689
As for Chenxi,

667
00:36:13,690 --> 00:36:15,559
I have already spoken with Xie Yuan.

668
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:17,119
As long as
it does not involve litigation,

669
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:18,610
I can continue to help there.

670
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,530
You have finally

671
00:36:20,770 --> 00:36:22,240
said this.

672
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:24,599
And I am truly grateful to you.

673
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:26,439
You gave me the opportunity

674
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:28,170
to discover the appeal
of non-litigation work.

675
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,599
You made me realize

676
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:31,559
that the mountaintop
is not just about the view,

677
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:32,840
there are also strong winds.

678
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,209
But I believe

679
00:36:34,210 --> 00:36:36,650
what suits me best is what matters most.

680
00:36:37,330 --> 00:36:39,170
Regarding Mr. Ren's case,

681
00:36:39,290 --> 00:36:40,769
you were treated unfairly.

682
00:36:40,770 --> 00:36:42,889
I intended to transfer you back quickly,

683
00:36:42,890 --> 00:36:45,050
but I did not expect you
to find a new direction.

684
00:36:45,650 --> 00:36:47,209
All these opportunities came from you,

685
00:36:47,210 --> 00:36:48,809
and they are still Ronghe's cases,

686
00:36:48,810 --> 00:36:50,880
just in a different practice area.

687
00:36:51,770 --> 00:36:54,570
Non-litigation
is not an easy path either.

688
00:36:54,650 --> 00:36:56,169
If you run into any difficulties later,

689
00:36:56,170 --> 00:36:57,490
come directly to me.

690
00:36:57,650 --> 00:36:58,800
Okay.

691
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,840
Everything is settled.

692
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:07,530
How is it going at the High Court?
Is everything smooth?

693
00:37:09,250 --> 00:37:10,720
I am not going
to the High Court anymore.

694
00:37:11,370 --> 00:37:12,610
Why?

695
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:15,240
Did the court make
some other arrangement?

696
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,809
Everyone has already reported in.

697
00:37:16,810 --> 00:37:18,289
The court could make
a special exception,

698
00:37:18,290 --> 00:37:19,919
but every position is already filled.

699
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:21,399
I would feel awkward

700
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:23,530
asking for special treatment.

701
00:37:25,850 --> 00:37:26,849
It is okay.

702
00:37:26,850 --> 00:37:29,170
We will try again next year.
There is still a chance.

703
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:32,130
I will not apply next year either.

704
00:37:33,330 --> 00:37:34,970
I plan to stay in the Family Court.

705
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,170
Why?

706
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:38,809
I used to admire

707
00:37:38,810 --> 00:37:40,530
the rational wisdom
of collective judgment.

708
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:43,400
I thought cases at the High Court
were more complex,

709
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:46,809
more representative and instructive,
able to contribute to the integrity of the law

710
00:37:46,810 --> 00:37:48,329
and the course of history,

711
00:37:48,330 --> 00:37:49,920
and influence more people.

712
00:37:50,290 --> 00:37:51,880
But during this time,

713
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,559
my experience in the Family Court

714
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:55,249
has shown me that each individual

715
00:37:55,250 --> 00:37:56,999
has different needs and struggles.

716
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,039
Only after experiencing

717
00:37:58,040 --> 00:38:00,010
all the bitterness,
hardship, and warmth,

718
00:38:00,170 --> 00:38:02,010
can understanding become complete.

719
00:38:02,650 --> 00:38:05,360
I want to become a truly good judge.

720
00:38:06,290 --> 00:38:09,090
There is no better place than this
to grow and be tested.

721
00:38:10,370 --> 00:38:12,280
Are you running a fever?

722
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:14,649
Or is something wrong with my ears?

723
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:16,690
This does not sound like
something you would say.

724
00:38:17,370 --> 00:38:17,959
What is it?

725
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,519
After staying
in the hospital for a while,

726
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,479
you have grown.

727
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:21,479
I know you have always enjoyed

728
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,090
arguing cases in court.

729
00:38:23,730 --> 00:38:24,729
If one day you want

730
00:38:24,730 --> 00:38:26,720
to return to litigation work,

731
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,880
anywhere outside Qingcheng District,

732
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:30,329
you can apply.

733
00:38:30,330 --> 00:38:31,690
We would not be in conflict.

734
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:36,320
Actually, the reason
I chose non-litigation

735
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:38,490
was because I was worried
you might think this way.

736
00:38:38,770 --> 00:38:40,210
Shen Xiezhi,

737
00:38:40,690 --> 00:38:42,280
I chose non-litigation

738
00:38:42,290 --> 00:38:43,689
not because of you.

739
00:38:43,690 --> 00:38:44,519
So I hope

740
00:38:44,520 --> 00:38:45,999
no matter when or for what reason,

741
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,570
even if it is because of me,

742
00:38:47,890 --> 00:38:49,760
you will still stick to your ideals.

743
00:38:49,890 --> 00:38:51,210
Do not give up.

744
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,240
Besides,

745
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:57,209
someone as capable as me

746
00:38:57,210 --> 00:38:59,280
can make a living anywhere.

747
00:39:00,370 --> 00:39:02,320
That is the Qin Rui I know.

748
00:39:03,650 --> 00:39:05,369
No matter what you choose
to do in the future,

749
00:39:05,370 --> 00:39:06,840
I will support you.

750
00:39:08,770 --> 00:39:10,209
I have a small gift for you.

751
00:39:10,210 --> 00:39:11,210
Wait for me.

752
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:15,429
♪And cast away my disguise♪

753
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:19,769
♪Lean on my tender shoulder♪

754
00:39:19,770 --> 00:39:21,010
What is this?

755
00:39:21,120 --> 00:39:22,400
Xiezhi?

756
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,959
At first, its horn was broken.

757
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:26,249
The shop assistant even worried
they were selling me a defective piece.

758
00:39:26,250 --> 00:39:27,689
At the time, I felt

759
00:39:27,690 --> 00:39:29,079
that in others' eyes,

760
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:30,729
I must have been like
this broken-horned Xiezhi,

761
00:39:30,730 --> 00:39:31,519
incomplete.

762
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:33,170
So I bought it

763
00:39:33,370 --> 00:39:34,720
and had it repaired.

764
00:39:35,810 --> 00:39:37,840
Now I want to give this Xiezhi to you.

765
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,599
I want to thank you,

766
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,090
for making my life feel whole.

767
00:39:44,120 --> 00:39:45,690
Will you take it?

768
00:39:49,330 --> 00:39:51,440
I will definitely treasure

769
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:54,690
this one-of-a-kind Xiezhi.

770
00:39:58,010 --> 00:39:59,569
♪I've decided♪

771
00:39:59,570 --> 00:40:02,940
♪To stay by your side♪

772
00:40:04,710 --> 00:40:08,229
♪I want to be in your world♪

773
00:40:08,230 --> 00:40:10,689
♪Everything is no longer faraway♪

774
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:14,890
(Six months later)

775
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,999
Lili,

776
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,689
I have put the documents here for you.

777
00:40:17,690 --> 00:40:18,720
Got it.

778
00:40:22,330 --> 00:40:24,730
(Judicial Document)

779
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,439
(So many important moments in life,)

780
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:34,130
(happen in an instant.)

781
00:40:34,650 --> 00:40:36,280
(In the Family Court,)

782
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:38,519
(I have been part of many such moments.)

783
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:39,519
Thank you.

784
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:41,769
(They have come together to form the most
meaningful moments of my life.)

785
00:40:41,770 --> 00:40:43,889
- Please pass this to Ms. Shu. Thank you.
- No problem.

786
00:40:43,890 --> 00:40:46,439
I was just about to look for you.
This just came down from above. Take a look.

787
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,570
Okay.

788
00:40:50,570 --> 00:40:54,130
(Meeting Room In Use)

789
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:57,400
(As a judge in the Family Court,)

790
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,169
(I once thought my duty)

791
00:40:59,170 --> 00:41:02,760
(was simply to deliver fair judgments
and final decisions.)

792
00:41:03,210 --> 00:41:04,959
(But through all of this,)

793
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,479
(I have witnessed right and wrong)

794
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,530
(turn into the power of reconciliation,)

795
00:41:08,850 --> 00:41:11,400
(and the possibility
within human emotions.)

796
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,280
(I have come to realize)

797
00:41:14,370 --> 00:41:15,849
(that emotion and reason,)

798
00:41:15,850 --> 00:41:17,439
(family and law,)

799
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:19,289
(and the distance
between us and the court,)

800
00:41:19,290 --> 00:41:21,880
(sometimes is only
the distance between hearts.)

801
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:24,959
(My duty is to bridge that distance,)

802
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:26,919
(to heal wounded hearts,)

803
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,769
(to resolve social conflicts,)

804
00:41:28,770 --> 00:41:31,010
(and mend emotional fractures.)

805
00:41:31,370 --> 00:41:33,439
(Office. Changing Room)
(To preserve this small warmth,)

806
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:35,880
(and safeguard
the warmth of the rule of law.)

807
00:41:36,810 --> 00:41:40,439
(Here, what I have seen and experienced)

808
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:43,800
(are the most hidden emotional ties,)

809
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:46,690
(complex entanglements of interests,)

810
00:41:46,810 --> 00:41:49,440
(the harsh tests of human nature,)

811
00:41:49,770 --> 00:41:53,010
(and the bonds
that are hardest to let go.)

812
00:41:54,290 --> 00:41:55,760
(Now,)

813
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:58,209
(Authorized Representative. Plaintiff)
(this has also become)

814
00:41:58,210 --> 00:42:00,199
(Defendant. Authorized Representative)
(the most important place in my life.)

815
00:42:00,199 --> 00:42:01,000
(Presiding Judge)

816
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:01,769
(Courtroom No. 1 In Session)

817
00:42:01,770 --> 00:42:03,410
(Hearing in progress)

818
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:05,650
All rise.

819
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:08,959
Please welcome the panel judge.

820
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:14,249
(Panel Judge)

821
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:16,249
(Family Court)
Please welcome the panel judge.

822
00:42:16,250 --> 00:42:18,490
Please welcome the panel judge.

823
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:22,169
♪Where right and wrong find their place♪

824
00:42:22,170 --> 00:42:28,440
♪Walking this road together,
still hoping♪

825
00:42:29,210 --> 00:42:34,670
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

826
00:42:36,170 --> 00:42:38,130
(Panel Judge)

827
00:42:40,730 --> 00:42:41,920
Please be seated.

828
00:42:44,230 --> 00:42:46,809
♪Where fairness stands♪

829
00:42:46,810 --> 00:42:47,769
Court is now in session.

830
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:48,559
Court is now in session.

831
00:42:48,560 --> 00:42:49,649
Court is now in session.

832
00:42:49,650 --> 00:42:50,920
Court is now in session.

833
00:42:54,210 --> 00:42:55,610
Court is now in session.

834
00:43:02,210 --> 00:43:05,410
(The End)

835
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

836
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

837
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

838
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

839
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

840
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

841
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

842
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

843
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

844
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

845
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

846
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

847
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

848
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

849
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

850
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

851
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

852
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

853
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

854
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

855
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

856
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

857
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:37,310
♪All the little things♪

858
00:44:37,310 --> 00:44:40,010
♪Woven into our lives♪

859
00:44:40,830 --> 00:44:42,880
♪The building blocks of life♪

860
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:44,590
♪Shape the sky above us♪

861
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:47,040
♪Are you doing alright?♪

862
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,150
♪What are you struggling for?♪

863
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,530
♪Some questions♪

864
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:54,800
♪Weigh like mountains♪

865
00:44:57,690 --> 00:45:02,840
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

866
00:45:03,120 --> 00:45:07,130
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

867
00:45:07,310 --> 00:45:12,360
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

868
00:45:12,730 --> 00:45:16,430
♪Where fairness stands♪

869
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:19,680
♪Within the law♪

870
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:29,520
♪And within every heart♪
